desc: Paws, Claws, & Cocktails - For a Cause! (But also) a bunch of cats making our way through NOLA bar life one paw in front of the other. NOLA Bar Cats strives to help other wayward cats throughout the community by pledging 10% of its annual profits to local cat rescues.
